<p>This page explains how to manage your privacy choices for Simbi: Bedtime Stories.</p>

<h2>Request account deletion</h2>
<p>If you want to delete your Simbi account and associated personal data, you can:</p>
<ol>
	<li>Use the account deletion option inside the app, if available</li>
	<li>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@getsimbi.com">support@getsimbi.com</a></li>
</ol>
<p>When we process a valid deletion request, we will delete or anonymize your account data unless we must retain certain information for legal, tax, fraud-prevention, or security reasons.</p>

<h2>Request access or correction</h2>
<p>You may contact us at <a href="mailto:support@getsimbi.com">support@getsimbi.com</a> to:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Request a copy of your personal data</li>
	<li>Correct inaccurate account information</li>
	<li>Ask questions about how your data is used</li>
</ul>

<h2>Child profiles</h2>
<p>Parents and guardians may request deletion of child profile information by contacting <a href="mailto:support@getsimbi.com">support@getsimbi.com</a>.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<div class="contact-block">
	<span class="contact-name">Matthew Smart</span>
	<span><a href="mailto:support@getsimbi.com">support@getsimbi.com</a></span>
</div>

</LegalPageLayout>
